data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!!! A 2-acre GEM in Rockwell! Starting outside, find space to park an RV, attached 2 car & detached 3 car garages, chicken coop, beautiful landscaping w/ mature trees, a solar station, new septic, and new roof! Step inside to an open floorplan, new flooring, vaulted ceiling in the living area, sunroom, kitchen w/ soaring center island, granite counter tops, gray cabinetry, elec cooktop, SS appliances installed in 2023 including wall-mounted oven/microwave combo, and a giant pantry. Dining space includes a breakfast room with bay window, master bedroom has oversized closet and ensuite bathroom with dual vanities, granite counter tops, jetted soaking tub, walk-in shower. Fully-finished basement perfect for independent living, income production, or just more space - family room, full kitchen, 2 bedrooms, and another full bath. Laundry rooms on both levels and plenty of flex space options for home office or gym. New HVAC sytem.And best of all, NO HOA!!!
